snippet.title: Cut the Rope - Remastered (Launch Trailer)
snippet.description:
Om Nom is back in the glorious 3D remaster of the internationally acclaimed Cut the Rope puzzle game! Featuring the most popular levels across the series as well as an abundance of brand new levels and content, players will cut ropes, avoid obstacles and use power ups to deliver candy to Om Nom, the little green monster that loves sweets. Do you want to play?

Download Cut the Rope Remastered Game in Apple Arcade! 
http://apple.co/-CutTheRopeR 

#CutTheRopeRemastered #OmNom #AppleArcade
